Malaysia Airlines (MAS) have given assurances that it has never hidden any information regarding the disappearance of its Boeing 777-200ER airplane, flight MH370. In an exclusive interview with Chinese broadcaster CCTV, MAS CEO Datuk Ahmad Jauhari Yahya also said search efforts will not cease until it is found. “We, and I think many others, are equally puzzled why we are unable to locate it,” he said.